SetInitialFeeTest
├── when caller is not fee manager
│   └── it should revert with "NFM"
└── when caller is fee manager
    ├── when pool does not exist
    │   └── it should revert
    └── when pool exists
        ├── when fee exceeds MAX_FEE_CAP and is not ZERO_FEE_INDICATOR
        │   └── it should revert with "MIF"
        └── when fee is valid
            ├── it should set initialFeeEnabled to true
            ├── it should set initialFee
            └── it should emit an {InitialFeeSet} event
